PROJETO-DE-PESQUISA.DESCRICAO-DO-PROJETO:
This project congregates the joint efforts of researches of two major centers Porto Alegre and GrenoblE (PAGE) in the areas of Parallel Processing. The main topics of interest are concentrated in:

    1. Implementation of parallel packages, e.g. Athapascan;
    2. Development of software tools to aid the parallel programing, e.g. Pajé;
    3. Development of modelling tools for parallel systems, e.g. PEPS;
